Serbia’s Cvetkovic to Take Responsibility for Finance Ministry

-- B y   G o r d a n a   F i l i p o v i c
-- 
2011-03-06T20:43:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-06/serbia-s-cvetkovic-to-take-responsibility-for-finance-ministry.html
Serbian Prime Minister  Mirko Cvetkovic  said tonight that he will take responsibility for the  finance ministry  in a shuffled cabinet, with the ministry
focusing on “development” in the government’s last year.  Cvetkovic, speaking in a live interview with B92 TV
channel, also said the new law on ministries, submitted to
parliament, will “restrict ways in which members of the cabinet
will communicate with media.”  To contact the reporters on this story:
Gordana Filipovic in London at 
 gfilipovic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  